**Asm2SMT** produces a symbolic representation of an AsmetaL model.<br/>
<h3>Download</h3>
<p>Download the tool: <a
 href="http://svn.code.sf.net/p/asmeta/code/code/experimental/smtRepresentation/translatorToSMT/AsmToSMT.jar">AsmToSMT.jar</a></p>
<h3>How to run<br/>
</h3>
To run Asm2SMT
<pre>java -jar Asm2SMT.jar asmetalFileName.asm</pre>


## Paper
P. Arcaini, A. Gargantini, E. Riccobene. SMT for state-based formal methods: the ASM case study, in 6th workshop on Automated Formal Methods (AFM 2017) [doi](https://doi.org/10.29007/djdz)
